---
name: Translated (Hebrew)
description: Style preset — Translated (Hebrew)
tags: [style, language, aspect-auto]
---
Render with all text labels translated to Hebrew. Preserve all diagram structure, shapes, arrows, and layout -- but replace every English text label with its Hebrew translation. Hebrew text should read right-to-left and use clear, modern Hebrew typography. Ensure translated labels fit naturally within their shapes and containers. Use clean, professional styling with colorful icons and clear visual hierarchy on a clean white background. The result should be a fully Hebrew-language version that reads naturally for a Hebrew speaker.
